**Post Office Time Deposit (TD)** offers government-backed fixed returns with quarterly compounding, making it comparable to bank FDs but with sovereign guarantee. The 5-year TD at 7.5% p.a. also qualifies for tax deduction under Section 80C up to ₹1.5 lakh, similar to a tax-saver bank FD.
